            "body": "I'm running into the same issue; this breaks all of my custom language server configs, which I enable prior to `nvim-lspconfig` like so:\n\n```\n-- enable language servers with custom configs\n---@type string[]\nlocal configured_servers = vim.iter(\n\tvim.api.nvim_get_runtime_file(\"after/lsp/*.lua\", true)\n)\n\t:filter(\n\t\t---@param file string\n\t\tfunction(file)\n\t\t\treturn vim.startswith(file, vim.fs.joinpath(vim.env.XDG_CONFIG_HOME, \"nvim\"))\n\t\tend\n\t)\n\t:map(\n\t\t---@param file string\n\t\tfunction(file)\n\t\t\treturn vim.fn.fnamemodify(file, \":t:r\")\n\t\tend\n\t)\n\t:totable()\nvim.lsp.enable(configured_servers)\n```",
